<div class="card text-center">
  <div class="card-header">
   <div class="text-center">
    <h3 class="display-4">Action Items Dashboard</h3>
   </div>
  </div>
  <div class="card-body">
    <p class="card-text" align="justify">The Action items system supports marketing campaigns that allow Dell to reengage customers who have abandoned their carts through email. A series of microservices across cart and personalization communicates with each other through HTTP as well as AMQP to allow for the events to be processed accordingly. Events are stored in a Postgres database to allow persistence of up to four weeks. This fully featured web-based UI contains supporting APIs on top of the existing database that allows for all analytical as well as management tasks of the action items events data.</p>
